Debugging with h2 :
java -cp lib/h2.jar org.h2.tools.Server
Then open the web browser to http://localhost:8082/ (if it does not open automatically)

Debugging with jdb :
java -Xdebug -Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_socket,address=8000,server=y,suspend=y -jar rel/hanzitrainer.jar
and
jdb -attach 8000

